                            <h4>Details: How "Bet a Friend or Play for a Cause" Works</h4>
                            <p>We'll send email notices to you and the potential recipient or charity twice: 
                            <br> &nbsp &nbsp • Immediately (Prior to the first day of the challenge)
                            <br> &nbsp &nbsp • Within Two Days After the challenge period ends to detail what you owe them, if anything.
                            </p>
                            <p>
                            If you end up "owing" your potential recipient or charity, paypal is quick and easy, but a mailed personal check could work as well. 
                            For listed charities, we will provide you with their donation-related web address and physical mailing address. 
                            </p>
                            <p>
                            How will we know you made the payment to them? It's on the honor system, so we will not collect money or broker the transaction, but since we are sending notices to the recipient of what you'd owe, it should help you keep your word! </p>
